dct_title_s: London: Two maps. Side 1: Central with notes for visitors = Centre avec detailed touristiques = Zentrum mit Auskunft fuer Besucher. Side 2: Routes through with sports clubs and grounds = Routes a travers Londres avec liste de Clubs Sportifs = mit dem Auto durch London mit Verzeichnis der Sportvereine und-plaetze
dct_description_sm: W. & A.K. Johnston & G.W. Bacon Limited. Johnsoton and Bacon Publishers. Map on both sides. Recto: Side 1: Central = centre = Zentrum. (1:15,840), Inset: "underground". Verso: Side 2: Routes through = Routes a travers Londres = mit dem Auto durch London"(1:63,360). Ancillary map: "Plan of central Heathrow" (1:24,690). With street index. London guide in English, French and German. ISBN: 0717941752.
